{"tid":467202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港島柏柴石澗發現手榴彈 !!!!","createTime":"2017-11-13T09:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T09:43:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c022b392e4c8b5d600eb82ffcf035aa5d03abcbc","tid":467202,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"新增影片<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午有行山人士在港島大潭道行山期間，在柏架山上的引水道近柏柴石澗位置，發現一個約3吋乘4吋疑為手榴彈物體，於是報警，由於山路遙遠，爆炸品處理課人員今日近中午奉召前往處理，消防車及救護車亦到場戒備，人員先在山腳整理裝備，再沿山徑上山，預計行約1小時才到達石澗。暫未知手榴彈所屬年代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510553594_7bb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510553594_7bb5.jpg&h=68bda8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510553606_0d40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510553606_0d40.jpg&h=da47db88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510553622_54b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510553622_54b5.jpg&h=7a7b6921&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}